body:
`phrase` has the following syntax:

```json
{
  $search: {
     "index": <index name>, // optional, defaults to "default"
     "phrase": {
       "query": "<search-string>",
       "path": "<field-to-search>",
       "score": <options>,
       "slop": <distance-number>,
       "synonyms": "<synonyms-mapping-name>"
     }
  }
}
```
